{"version":1,"content":"<html>\n  <body><img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20260429/s00024/8331fd6c752d4497af6570423ab26558.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%;border-radius:6px;margin-bottom:1em\">\n    <p>男團MIRROR成員姜濤明日（4月30日）27歲生日，「姜濤香港後援會」連續第5年與香港電車合辦「4.30姜濤生日 電車免費乘車日」，讓市民免費搭電車。（資料以主辦方最新公布為準）</p>\n  </body>\n</html>","scraped_at":"2026-04-29T06:10:33.625613+00:00","quality":{"score":0,"chars":90,"images":1,"source":"明報 消閒","fallback":"none"}}